<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Ocean Explorer Website</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #e0f7fa;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    .hero-section {
      background-color: #006994;
      color: white;
      padding: 50px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .content-card {
      background-color: white;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    h2 {
      color: #006994;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #006994;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container-fluid hero-section">
    <h1 class="display-3">Deep Ocean Explorer</h1>
    <p class="lead">Dive in and discover the mysteries of the deep blue sea!</p>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      
      <div class="col-12 col-md-8 content-card">
        <h2>About the Ocean</h2>
        <p>The ocean covers more than <strong>70%</strong> of the surface of our planet. It is home to millions of species and produces over half of the world's oxygen. Even today, more than 80% of the ocean remains unexplored and unmapped!</p>
        
        <h2>Fascinating Marine Life</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Dolphins:</strong> Highly intelligent marine mammals known for their playful behavior.</li>
          <li><strong>Sea Turtles:</strong> Ancient reptiles that can migrate thousands of miles across the ocean.</li>
          <li><strong>Coral Reefs:</strong> Underwater ecosystems often called the "rainforests of the sea."</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
        <div class="content-card text-center">
          <h2>Did You Know?</h2>
          <p>The Pacific Ocean is the largest and deepest of Earth's oceanic divisions. It is larger than all of the Earth's land area combined!</p>
          <button class="btn btn-info mt-3">Learn More</button>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
